---
description: Autonomous testing and improvement loop.
alwaysApply: false
---

Run the app using fluttter run -d emulator-5554 in background, then wait 30 sec , then manually test everything working fine and the entire parsing logic from the app + group + cluster group is working fine and optimal (for ex : no labo , same medications correctly reunited , search optimal ...)

The testing process must concerns all the capacities, UI and UX from the codebase to construct a detailed report, page per page, of each suggestions, fixes and improvements in working logic/ui/ux. Do not stop until you've tried and verified everything.

For each issue / incoherence / error, implement the fix then enter into a fully autonomous loop of flutter run -> wait -> test -> fix until every thing is solved and the app is production ready.

Important : Do not test capacities related to camera (from the scanner). Only test library, research, parsing, group...
To access to the logs in real time, make sure to use talker capacities. No need to run flutter logs or any similar command.
